bio: Spiritual guidance you can count on
about:
Hi, I’m Tamara, from Australia 💙🙏🔮
I am a renowned Tarot reader and interpreter (empath) of Romani gypsy descent as far back too India, my clan originated from India with 3 years + professional experience, i also receive direct messages from spirit (Clairessence/Clairaudient)
(i have had an interest in tarot, divination and spirituality for as long as I can remember due to my upbringing)

I am also a qualified holistic counselor which I believe is such a benefit, especially when doing in-depth reads. 
I use my own intuition to pick my cards from a few of my traditional decks or oracle and receive direct messages from spirit at times. 
💙💙💙
I am an indigo/starseed.
As a child I amazed my grandparents with my intuition and being able to see auras and energies from a very young age, I also obtained my Reiki II at the young age of nine due to my spiritual upbringing, my grandmother is a reiki master, tarot reader, psychic and spiritualist guide
(Romani Gypsy) 
And also my coach 
💙💙💙
so I was very much brought up to be spiritually aware.
Since I have been awoken, I have been studying the meanings and interpretations of Tarot cards and how to interpret messages from spirit concisely . 🔮🌈🙏
I have had great success through social media outlets, different platforms and am continually am receiving positive feedback, with a full star rating.
💙💙💙
I believe my reads are very different because of how empathetic I am and honest-I do not like to sugar coat, whilst also having the ability to offer counselling through our reading sessions, which is a major bonus for myself and the reader.
💙💙💙
To conduct our readings I ask the universe/spirit for guidance and shuffle my deck until a card pops out at me, we will the explore the interpretation of the card In a simple to understand context, In some cases spirit will talk to me directly and send me direct messages
